{
  "title": "Readyset \u00b7 Strapi FoodAdvisor \u2014 Live Demo",
  "uid": "readyset-foodadvisor",
  "description": "Readyset caching Strapi FoodAdvisor on Postgres. Before caching: everything falls through to Postgres. After CREATE CACHE: p95 drops, rows-fetched drops, cache hit rate \u2192 100%.",
